org.apache.juneau.urlencoding

Class UonParserContext

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.juneau.Context
      • org.apache.juneau.parser.ParserContext
        • org.apache.juneau.urlencoding.UonParserContext
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    UrlEncodingParserContext

    public class UonParserContext
extends ParserContext
    Configurable properties on the UonParser class.

    Context properties are set by calling ContextFactory.setProperty(String, Object) on the context factory returned CoreApi.getContextFactory().

    The following convenience methods are also provided for setting context properties:

    • UonParser.setProperty(String,Object)
    • UonParser.setProperties(ObjectMap)
    • UonParser.addNotBeanClasses(Class[])
    • UonParser.addBeanFilters(Class[])
    • UonParser.addPojoSwaps(Class[])
    • UonParser.addImplClass(Class,Class)

    See ContextFactory for more information about context properties.

    Author:
    James Bognar (james.bognar@salesforce.com)

    • Field Detail

      • UON_decodeChars

        public static final String UON_decodeChars
        Decode "%xx" sequences. (Boolean, default=false for UonParser, true for UrlEncodingParser).

        Specify true if URI encoded characters should be decoded, false if they've already been decoded before being passed to this parser.
